  title: "30.5 Automatic Stabilizers"
  domain: "economia_faculdade"
  definition: "Ao final desta secao, voce sera capaz de: Describe how the federal government can use discretionary fiscal policy to stabilize the economy; Identify examples of automatic stabilizers; Understand how a government can use standardized employment budget to identify automatic stabilizers."
