  title: "30.6 Practical Problems with Discretionary Fiscal Policy"
  domain: "economia_faculdade"
  definition: "Ao final desta secao, voce sera capaz de: Understand how fiscal policy and monetary policy are interconnected; Explain the three lag times that often occur when solving economic problems; Identify the legal and political challenges of responding to an economic problem."
  requires: [eco.30-5-automatic-stabilizers.v1]
  interactivity: 5
  decay_rate: 0.03
