KNOWLEDGE eco.30-7-the-question-of-a-balanced-budget.v1 INTERMEDIATE {
  title: "30.7 The Question of a Balanced Budget"
  domain: "economia_faculdade"
  definition: "Ao final desta secao, voce sera capaz de: Understand the arguments for and against requiring the U.S. federal budget to be balanced; Consider the long-run and short-run effects of a federal budget deficit."
