  domain: "economia_faculdade"
  definition: "Ao final desta secao, voce sera capaz de: Analyze the growth policies of low-income countries seeking to improve standards of living; Analyze the growth policies of middle-income countries, particularly the East Asian Tigers with their focus on technology and market-oriented incentives; Analyze the struggles facing economically-challenged countries wishing to enact growth policies; Evaluate the success of sending aid to low-income countries."
