  domain: "economia_faculdade"
  definition: "Ao final desta secao, voce sera capaz de: Explain the nature and causes of unemployment; Analyze the natural rate of unemployment and the factors that affect it; Identify how undeveloped labor markets can result in the same hardships as unemployment."
