  title: "34.4 How Governments Enact Trade Policy: Globally, Regionally, and Nationally"
  domain: "economia_faculdade"
  definition: "Ao final desta secao, voce sera capaz de: Explain the origin and role of the World Trade Organization (WTO) and General Agreement on Tariffs and Trade (GATT); Discuss the significance and provide examples of regional trading agreements; Analyze trade policy at the national level; Evaluate long-term trends in barriers to trade."
